{
  "title": "Xtra Savory Mexican Potatoes Skillet",
  "description": "A savory and springy one-pot Mexican dish featuring Jersey Royal potatoes and ferment-kimchi, made FODMAP-friendly for all to enjoy. This recipe combines the flavors of Mexico with the spice of kimchi.",
  "cuisine": "Mexican",
